1
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Too tired to walk anymore.</font>

2
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can't believe you're gone, Mihai...</font>

3
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're sending us into
a dangerous hotspot tomorrow.</font>

4
00:00:25,460 --> 00:00:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I get the feeling I won't make it out alive.</font>

5
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here to drag me back home?</font>

6
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No.</font>

7
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm here to wait on you as usual, milady.</font>

8
00:00:47,130 --> 00:00:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

9
00:00:48,540 --> 00:00:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's my job as your manservant, after all.</font>

10
00:02:23,580 --> 00:02:28,500
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}EPISODE 11: SNEAK ATTACK</b></font>

11
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aw, jeez! Just go home already!</font>

12
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here, Lady Cecil.</font>

13
00:02:38,460 --> 00:02:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A little something to satisfy your appetite.</font>

14
00:02:57,830 --> 00:03:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm not crying, you hear me!</font>

15
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:01,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Of course.</font>

16
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Say, Allen? My brother was strong, wasn't he?</font>

17
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes.</font>

18
00:03:08,170 --> 00:03:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I was never able to beat him.</font>

19
00:03:14,790 --> 00:03:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll be frank.</font>

20
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The thought of dying is scary to me.</font>

21
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Terrifyingly so.</font>

22
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I just want to go home to my family.</font>

23
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm gonna die, too. I just know it...</font>

24
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I don't wanna!</font>

25
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:37,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lady Cecil.</font>

26
00:03:39,330 --> 00:03:41,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Will you like to come with me
and leave the city behind?</font>

27
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:42,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

28
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just forget about your family. We can be free
to travel the world and visit all sorts of places.</font>

29
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Have you gone crazy? You know we can't do that!</font>

30
00:03:53,380 --> 00:03:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then shall we wait until next year?</font>

31
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We can register as adventurers after we become 12.</font>

32
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah, right. I'll be enrolled
in the Academy by then...</font>

33
00:04:01,420 --> 00:04:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Who says you have to go? It's only a school.</font>

34
00:04:04,670 --> 00:04:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

35
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's your life, isn't it?
You should choose how you want to live it.</font>

36
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What do you want to do, Lady Cecil?</font>

37
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What I want? I'm not sure...</font>

38
00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">At the end of the day, I'm not doing this
for the people or even my family.</font>

39
00:04:22,250 --> 00:04:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm here because I chose to be here.</font>

40
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Allen. We're going home now.</font>

41
00:04:35,170 --> 00:04:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">As you wish.</font>

42
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey.</font>

43
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hm?</font>

44
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My legs hurt. Carry me.</font>

45
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay.</font>

46
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Allen?</font>

47
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes? What is it?</font>

48
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you.</font>

49
00:04:52,170 --> 00:04:53,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't mention it.</font>

50
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cecil!</font>

51
00:04:58,580 --> 00:04:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Father...</font>

52
00:05:00,210 --> 00:05:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cecil!</font>

53
00:05:01,130 --> 00:05:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cecil!</font>

54
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sorry for being a bad girl...</font>

55
00:05:04,790 --> 00:05:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Listen, Cecil. I don't want you
to worry about anything.</font>

56
00:05:08,540 --> 00:05:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

57
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In the near future,
we'll be able to mine mithril again.</font>

58
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then we can get you an exemption
from the Noble's Duty</font>

59
00:05:16,130 --> 00:05:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">by gifting the royal family
with the mining rights.</font>

60
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll handle all the negotiations myself.</font>

61
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So rest easy!</font>

62
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's why he's been in a rush
to get the mines running.</font>

63
00:05:27,210 --> 00:05:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Father. Mother.</font>

64
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">As a member of the Granvelle household,</font>

65
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I shall meet my obligation
to serve the Noble's Duty.</font>

66
00:05:37,540 --> 00:05:41,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The whole reason that I came here
was to overcome my own weakness.</font>

67
00:05:42,710 --> 00:05:44,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am going to follow in Mihai's footsteps.</font>

68
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I won't flee from responsibility!</font>

69
00:05:57,670 --> 00:06:00,460
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ALLEN: AGE 11</b></font>

70
00:05:57,670 --> 00:06:00,460
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}MARCH</b></font>

71
00:06:05,670 --> 00:06:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">B-rank magic stone secured!</font>

72
00:06:08,630 --> 00:06:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Half a year has passed since Mihai's death.</font>

73
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Life for the Granvelles has gone back to normal.</font>

74
00:06:13,250 --> 00:06:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And the Knighthood has wiped out
all the orc boroughs.</font>

75
00:06:16,290 --> 00:06:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, mostly because me and my team
did the dirty work.</font>

76
00:06:21,130 --> 00:06:25,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We've finally started moving people to resettle
the mithril refineries near the mines, eh?</font>

77
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mining operations should be running
at full steam come summer.</font>

78
00:06:28,380 --> 00:06:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This should put the baron's mind at ease.</font>

79
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The only problem now... is whether Carnel
will lash out after losing his mithril.</font>

80
00:06:35,290 --> 00:06:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">His silence so far is actually concerning.</font>

81
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Stay vigilant.</font>

82
00:06:39,580 --> 00:06:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yessir.</font>

83
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Despite what she says,
there's no way Cecil could climb this mountain.</font>

84
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Take me with you! I'm going hunting, too!</font>

85
00:06:51,710 --> 00:06:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I sympathize with the fact
she wants to toughen up,</font>

86
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but the baron will never allow it.</font>

87
00:06:56,580 --> 00:07:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Having long-range support
from a Wizardess would be nice, though.</font>

88
00:07:06,330 --> 00:07:07,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I made it!</font>

89
00:07:08,210 --> 00:07:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">These guys could cause problems
for the mithril miners.</font>

90
00:07:10,580 --> 00:07:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So I'm gonna wipe them out next!</font>

91
00:07:13,130 --> 00:07:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">From what I've heard about Armored Ant nests,
there should be over 1,000 soldiers inside</font>

92
00:07:16,790 --> 00:07:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">along with a B-rank queen monster
who lays eggs to birth more.</font>

93
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's not a lot of info to go on.</font>

94
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And I can't get a look at the layout from the sky.</font>

95
00:07:26,540 --> 00:07:30,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's only one entrance.
Just big enough for a single ant to pass through.</font>

96
00:07:30,460 --> 00:07:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'd get swarmed if I tried
to fight them inside the nest.</font>

97
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Should I trim their numbers
before I try to breach?</font>

98
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, nothing like a good challenge!
We'll just wing it!</font>

99
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll start with a team of six.</font>

100
00:07:40,330 --> 00:07:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Teddy! Spidey! Fillet!</font>

101
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yikes. They just keep coming.</font>

102
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Get out here, everybody!</font>

103
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Alright! Give 'em hell!</font>

104
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,670
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ONE MONTH LATER</b></font>

105
00:08:13,420 --> 00:08:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's been a whole month
and I still can't beat this ant colony...</font>

106
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've come twice a week and taken down over 200
ants per day, which means about 2,000 total.</font>

107
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:22,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So what's the deal?</font>

108
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Not to mention, all the corpses
of the defeated ants are cleared out</font>

109
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">by the time I come back the week after.</font>

110
00:08:27,790 --> 00:08:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is the queen eating them and laying new eggs?</font>

111
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:39,790
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 ARMORED ANT.</b></font>

112
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:39,790
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE GAINED 30,000 EXP.</b></font>

113
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:39,790
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 ARMORED ANT.</b></font>

114
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:39,790
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE GAINED 30,000 EXP.</b></font>

115
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:39,790
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 ARMORED ANT.</b></font>

116
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:39,790
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE GAINED 30,000 EXP.</b></font>

117
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:39,790
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 ARMORED ANT.</b></font>

118
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:39,790
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE GAINED 30,000 EXP.</b></font>

119
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I love all this delicious EXP,</font>

120
00:08:34,290 --> 00:08:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but the endless stream of ants
is blocking me from entering the nest</font>

121
00:08:36,710 --> 00:08:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and I can't even collect their magic stones!</font>

122
00:08:39,790 --> 00:08:44,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ANOTHER MONTH LATER</b></font>

123
00:08:40,210 --> 00:08:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've gotta change my strategy.</font>

124
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:46,250
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 ARMORED ANT.</b></font>

125
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:46,250
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE GAINED 30,000 EXP.</b></font>

126
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:46,250
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 ARMORED ANT.</b></font>

127
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:46,250
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE GAINED 30,000 EXP.</b></font>

128
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:46,250
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 ARMORED ANT.</b></font>

129
00:08:44,050 --> 00:08:46,250
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE GAINED 30,000 EXP.</b></font>

130
00:08:47,580 --> 00:08:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bruh. I've killed 5,000 of these damned things.</font>

131
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Am I just gonna have to camp out here every day?</font>

132
00:08:56,170 --> 00:08:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Really wish they'd let me
be a Huntsman full time...</font>

133
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? What the-?!</font>

134
00:09:04,290 --> 00:09:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They stopped! Has my persistence paid off?!</font>

135
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Time to stamp out the queen.</font>

136
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Come on out, Hollow!</font>

137
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,170
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}BIRD D</b></font>

138
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,170
<font size="21"><b>{\an7}AGILITY +20, INTELLIGENCE +20</b></font>

139
00:09:19,250 --> 00:09:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Do your thing!</font>

140
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Vision sharing with Hollow activated.</font>

141
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank God for night vision.</font>

142
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This place is like a huge maze.</font>

143
00:09:32,670 --> 00:09:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh crap! An ambush!</font>

144
00:09:36,170 --> 00:09:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's try that again.</font>

145
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ew! There's the egg chamber!</font>

146
00:09:42,330 --> 00:09:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pull back!</font>

147
00:09:44,290 --> 00:09:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now I'll send one the other way.</font>

148
00:09:46,580 --> 00:09:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And have another Hollow check out this passageway.</font>

149
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Controlling eight at once is mentally exhausting.</font>

150
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Man, I could really use some chocolate...</font>

151
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:02,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Feels like playing one of those
long-ass mini-games in an RPG.</font>

152
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:06,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The sun's going down, so I should head home soon.</font>

153
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I can't pass up this chance...</font>

154
00:10:11,210 --> 00:10:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thar she blows!</font>

155
00:10:13,380 --> 00:10:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Alright! Time to end this!</font>

156
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Finally, after two months of grinding.</font>

157
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Queen Armored Ant!</font>

158
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Look at that! She's like
three times the size of a normal one!</font>

159
00:10:30,290 --> 00:10:32,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, except for the head, I guess...</font>

160
00:10:35,170 --> 00:10:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Alright, we all know how boss fights go.</font>

161
00:10:37,250 --> 00:10:39,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Defeat the small fries first, Teddy squad!</font>

162
00:10:49,210 --> 00:10:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sweet! Now all that's left is the queen.</font>

163
00:10:57,290 --> 00:10:58,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shit.</font>

164
00:10:58,210 --> 00:11:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I can summon them faster
than she can beat them!</font>

165
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Teddy! Go for the abdomen!</font>

166
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sink those teeth into her!</font>

167
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">CHOMP LIKE NO TOMORROW!</font>

168
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:24,580
<font size="27" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 QUEEN ARMORED ANT.</b></font>

169
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:24,580
<font size="27" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE GAINED 45,000 EXP.</b></font>

170
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Only took me 20 summons to win, huh?</font>

171
00:11:28,210 --> 00:11:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I needed more than 100 to beat the Orc King.</font>

172
00:11:31,540 --> 00:11:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Maybe she was just super weak
after birthing all those extra soldier ants.</font>

173
00:11:35,710 --> 00:11:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can't go back to town at this late hour.
Gonna have to camp overnight.</font>

174
00:11:40,130 --> 00:11:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bet I'll get a serious earful for it later.</font>

175
00:11:43,710 --> 00:11:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Need to find something to prove
I wiped this place clean.</font>

176
00:11:50,710 --> 00:11:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait, is that...?</font>

177
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:57,000
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}THE HARDCORE GAMER DOMINATES</b></font>

178
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:57,000
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}IN ANOTHER WORLD WITH GARBAGE BALANCING</b></font>

179
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I brought this back from a nest
up in the White Dragon Mountains.</font>

180
00:12:02,460 --> 00:12:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's the exoskeleton of a Queen Armored Ant.</font>

181
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Weird...</font>

182
00:12:08,210 --> 00:12:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I thought this would be a big deal,
but they seem unfazed.</font>

183
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:16,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You went up the White Dragon Mountains?
At least make your stories somewhat believable.</font>

184
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's plausible. Armored ants
do come in different colors.</font>

185
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What do you think, Zenof?</font>

186
00:12:22,210 --> 00:12:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hard to say as I've never seen a queen myself.</font>

187
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

188
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I mean, not even the Knighthood has enough
resources to defeat an entire ant colony.</font>

189
00:12:30,670 --> 00:12:31,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What?!</font>

190
00:12:31,290 --> 00:12:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You didn't just slap a coat
of paint on it, did you?</font>

191
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">N-no way!</font>

192
00:12:34,630 --> 00:12:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Allen, my boy.</font>

193
00:12:36,170 --> 00:12:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Armored Ant colonies are filled
with thousands of soldiers.</font>

194
00:12:39,290 --> 00:12:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And the interior is a complex maze.</font>

195
00:12:41,630 --> 00:12:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That makes them nigh impossible to defeat.</font>

196
00:12:43,710 --> 00:12:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">True enough. It was really
only possible thanks to my summons.</font>

197
00:12:48,290 --> 00:12:51,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">W-well, I have one more thing to show you!</font>

198
00:12:52,330 --> 00:12:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I came across these in the chamber
where the queen ant was.</font>

199
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">M-my God! That's mithril ore!</font>

200
00:12:59,290 --> 00:13:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Certainly not something
that one just stumbles across.</font>

201
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Allen. Give us all the details.</font>

202
00:13:05,250 --> 00:13:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yessir!</font>

203
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So he was telling the truth...</font>

204
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:16,630
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}CARNEL FIEFDOM</b></font>

205
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:16,630
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}GRANVELLE FIEFDOM</b></font>

206
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The nest was around here.</font>

207
00:13:16,170 --> 00:13:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And this is a map of the interior.</font>

208
00:13:19,420 --> 00:13:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There is no doubt about it now.</font>

209
00:13:22,250 --> 00:13:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's found a fifth vein of mithril
for us to mine from.</font>

210
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll have my knights scope it out immediately.</font>

211
00:13:28,170 --> 00:13:31,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Superb work, Allen.
You've truly outdone yourself this time.</font>

212
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I will forgive your illicit overnight excursion.</font>

213
00:13:34,830 --> 00:13:36,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you, my lord.</font>

214
00:13:36,330 --> 00:13:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Furthermore,</font>

215
00:13:37,330 --> 00:13:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">you've become the first to discover a brand new
vein of mithril where this ore came from.</font>

216
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:46,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That entitles you to a stake in the operation.</font>

217
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I shall grant you a 30 percent
of the mining rights.</font>

218
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? The mining rights, my lord?</font>

219
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is bound to go over your head.</font>

220
00:13:54,130 --> 00:13:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But just give it a few years
and you'll start to understand the benefits.</font>

221
00:13:58,750 --> 00:13:59,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay.</font>

222
00:14:00,130 --> 00:14:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I get the feeling this is a huge deal...</font>

223
00:14:05,380 --> 00:14:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now it's October.</font>

224
00:14:06,630 --> 00:14:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And I've finally turned 12.</font>

225
00:14:09,380 --> 00:14:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Keep it up, fellas! Good work today.</font>

226
00:14:09,380 --> 00:14:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The mithril mines have
restarted after a century of unuse.</font>

227
00:14:13,130 --> 00:14:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But work on the vein that
I discovered won't start until next year.</font>

228
00:14:17,630 --> 00:14:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I have nothing to fear from
the monsters around here anymore.</font>

229
00:14:20,250 --> 00:14:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And I don't have to worry
about money thanks to my stake in the mines.</font>

230
00:14:23,420 --> 00:14:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That said...</font>

231
00:14:24,830 --> 00:14:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">something doesn't feel right.</font>

232
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:28,420
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}SEARCH</b></font>

233
00:14:27,540 --> 00:14:30,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This isn't the hardcore gaming I thrive on.</font>

234
00:14:28,420 --> 00:14:29,080
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}VIDEO GAME</b></font>

235
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,250
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}GARBAGE BALANCING</b></font>

236
00:14:30,250 --> 00:14:32,880
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}HARDCORE</b></font>

237
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wanna live on the edge! Not in comfort!</font>

238
00:14:33,130 --> 00:14:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's time to expand my horizons.</font>

239
00:14:35,420 --> 00:14:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll bring up the idea with the baron later.</font>

240
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aw jeez...</font>

241
00:14:39,290 --> 00:14:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Guess who's paying another visit?
The royal messenger is here.</font>

242
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:45,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ugh. What does he want this time?</font>

243
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeesh, talk about double trouble.</font>

244
00:14:52,630 --> 00:14:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Viscount Carnel is here, too.</font>

245
00:14:55,710 --> 00:14:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can already tell they're going to stir up shit.</font>

246
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Greetings, my good sirs.
May I ask what brings you here today?</font>

247
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I heard good news that the mithril mines
are up and running again.</font>

248
00:15:06,710 --> 00:15:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've come to present a proposal
for your consideration.</font>

249
00:15:12,330 --> 00:15:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Granvelle and Carnel fiefdoms</font>

250
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">have been trapped in an
endless cycle of prosperity</font>

251
00:15:16,330 --> 00:15:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and decline at the whims of the White Dragon.</font>

252
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The royal family seeks to solve
this problem once and for all.</font>

253
00:15:23,290 --> 00:15:24,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Unbelievable...</font>

254
00:15:24,750 --> 00:15:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're suggesting that we co-manage
the White Dragon Mountains?!</font>

255
00:15:28,460 --> 00:15:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? Is he for real?!</font>

256
00:15:31,290 --> 00:15:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Indeed.</font>

257
00:15:33,130 --> 00:15:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Both families shall manage the mining operations
and split all the profits equally.</font>

258
00:15:37,330 --> 00:15:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That should put an end to the turmoil of the past.</font>

259
00:15:40,540 --> 00:15:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I reached out to the Vice Minister of Justice
and had him draft that contract personally.</font>

260
00:15:45,210 --> 00:15:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Viscount Carnel has already
affixed his signature to it.</font>

261
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Heh.</font>

262
00:15:48,330 --> 00:15:50,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All we need now is yours.</font>

263
00:15:50,670 --> 00:15:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just look at that smug bastard.
He's obviously behind all of this.</font>

264
00:15:54,670 --> 00:15:56,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My deepest apologies.</font>

265
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm afraid this is too abrupt.</font>

266
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I must play it safe and visit the royal capital
to appraise the situation first.</font>

267
00:16:01,210 --> 00:16:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Say what?!</font>

268
00:16:02,330 --> 00:16:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You dare to suggest that I am untrustworthy?!</font>

269
00:16:05,040 --> 00:16:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am saying this is a critical decision that
I cannot in good conscience rush to make.</font>

270
00:16:09,130 --> 00:16:12,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The mithril profits have
clearly poisoned your mind!</font>

271
00:16:12,580 --> 00:16:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mark my words, your greed shall be your undoing!</font>

272
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We suffered for a century!</font>

273
00:16:22,500 --> 00:16:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And just when fortune finally swings our way,
they have the gall to demand half of it?!</font>

274
00:16:27,540 --> 00:16:30,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This contract is beyond outrageous!</font>

275
00:16:31,170 --> 00:16:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Captain Zenof is up in
the mountains right now, isn't he?</font>

276
00:16:34,330 --> 00:16:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes, milord. He is scheduled
to return in two days' time.</font>

277
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then we head for the royal capital
as soon as he's back.</font>

278
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, shoot. This makes it awkward for me to talk
to the baron about moving on from manservant...</font>

279
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let me get this straight.</font>

280
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A co-management contract means
the economy won't go downhill</font>

281
00:16:52,040 --> 00:16:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">even after the White Dragon migrates, right?</font>

282
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:57,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's right. We can never be sure when it
might come back to this side, anyways.</font>

283
00:16:57,500 --> 00:17:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sure, it sounds good on its face, but we can't
trust anything involving Viscount Carnel.</font>

284
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He'll stab us in the back for sure.</font>

285
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The problem is that we can't refuse
without coming off as greedy.</font>

286
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Can the baron even get out of this double bind?</font>

287
00:17:09,080 --> 00:17:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh no! Lady Cecil!</font>

288
00:17:10,540 --> 00:17:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's going on?</font>

289
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cecil!</font>

290
00:17:28,330 --> 00:17:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Friggin' brat.</font>

291
00:17:33,380 --> 00:17:35,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's the problem? Kill him already!</font>

292
00:17:35,420 --> 00:17:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This guy's tough.</font>

293
00:17:36,830 --> 00:17:38,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll have to change up my stock of cards.</font>

294
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:39,000
<font size="21" color="#feffdf"><b>{\an7}NAME: ALLEN</b></font>

