332
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Chickening out already, brat? Bring it on!</font>

333
00:17:41,580 --> 00:17:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Challenge accepted!</font>

334
00:17:45,830 --> 00:17:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's hitting a lot harder all of a sudden.</font>

335
00:17:48,170 --> 00:17:49,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Baron Granvelle!</font>

336
00:17:49,500 --> 00:17:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We're under attack!
Intruders have taken Lady Cecil!</font>

337
00:17:52,210 --> 00:17:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What?!</font>

338
00:17:55,290 --> 00:17:57,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Screw it! We're outta here!</font>

339
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cecil...</font>

340
00:18:15,210 --> 00:18:16,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cecil?!</font>

341
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank God. She's alive.</font>

342
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Those bastards tied me up extra tight.</font>

343
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But they don't know Summoners
can still fight as long as they can see!</font>

344
00:18:27,790 --> 00:18:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Chappy! Get out here!</font>

345
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Vision share!</font>

346
00:18:33,040 --> 00:18:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's the kidnappers from earlier.</font>

347
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Looks like we're inside a warehouse somewhere.</font>

348
00:18:38,040 --> 00:18:38,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oi!</font>

349
00:18:40,170 --> 00:18:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ya need something, Dagrah, sir?</font>

350
00:18:44,210 --> 00:18:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What you'd nab two kids for?</font>

351
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, the little guy knows how to wield a sword.</font>

352
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Figured we'd make some dough
selling him as a slave.</font>

353
00:18:55,170 --> 00:18:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You don't get to call the shots.
I'll gut you next time.</font>

354
00:18:58,540 --> 00:19:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Got it. Sorry...</font>

355
00:19:01,130 --> 00:19:03,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Kill the boy right away if he causes any problems.</font>

356
00:19:04,420 --> 00:19:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That guy is way more of a threat
than these clowns.</font>

357
00:19:06,250 --> 00:19:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You all right, Marcus?</font>

358
00:19:07,630 --> 00:19:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah. Bloody hell.</font>

359
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why'd the boss put that violent asshole
in charge? It's such bullshit.</font>

360
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cuz Dagrah's a combat pro who fought in the war.</font>

361
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pssht. More like he's a pussy
who ditched his post after a year.</font>

362
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dude. It's your funeral.</font>

363
00:19:21,830 --> 00:19:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In any case, he's the only one of us
who can fight Zenof.</font>

364
00:19:25,710 --> 00:19:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Zenof? They must be talking
about the knight captain.</font>

365
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But Zenof's a certified badass
who held the line at the fort for over a decade.</font>

366
00:19:32,210 --> 00:19:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Does Dagrah actually stand a chance against him?</font>

367
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hell if I know.</font>

368
00:19:35,330 --> 00:19:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I mean, Zenof still lost his entire squadron
by the time he came back, right?</font>

369
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Might as well just go down with 'em
at that point, yeah?</font>

370
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, whatever. War is for idiots
with a death wish, anyways.</font>

371
00:19:45,460 --> 00:19:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">You said it, man.</font>

372
00:19:45,460 --> 00:19:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Interesting.</font>

373
00:19:46,630 --> 00:19:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So, there really is some kinda war going on...</font>

374
00:19:49,330 --> 00:19:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Anyway, there's no sense waiting for rescue.
I can take these jerks.</font>

375
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:56,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, crap! I dropped my mithril sword!</font>

376
00:19:56,210 --> 00:19:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">These are all the weapons I have on me right now.</font>

377
00:19:58,250 --> 00:20:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm not confident that I can fight
and protect Cecil with just these.</font>

378
00:20:01,330 --> 00:20:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gonna go take a whizz.</font>

379
00:20:03,290 --> 00:20:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now's my chance!</font>

380
00:20:04,290 --> 00:20:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll start by scoping out an escape route.</font>

381
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whoa.</font>

382
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's a bird doing on the ship?</font>

383
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? Ship?</font>

384
00:20:11,170 --> 00:20:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Are we on a boat?</font>

385
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Nobody told me you could reach the sea
from the Granvelle fiefdom.</font>

386
00:20:16,580 --> 00:20:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Man, this ship is huge.</font>

387
00:20:19,130 --> 00:20:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's pitch-black outside. Already nighttime, huh?</font>

388
00:20:23,670 --> 00:20:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait a sec. Are we flying?</font>

389
00:20:26,580 --> 00:20:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This ain't a boat...</font>

390
00:20:28,290 --> 00:20:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">it's a magic ship!</font>

391
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, crap! How am I supposed
to escape in mid-air?!</font>

392
00:20:34,710 --> 00:20:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay, keep calm. There should still be
a chance when it descends.</font>

393
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:42,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow, there's even a restaurant?</font>

394
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This ship is bigger than I thought.</font>

395
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I recognize that stupid laugh.</font>

396
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Figures he was behind all this!</font>

397
00:20:51,130 --> 00:20:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You know what I expect, right?</font>

398
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I pulled a lot of strings
to set things up for you.</font>

399
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I presume you mean the mining rights?</font>

400
00:20:57,830 --> 00:20:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You shall have them on a silver platter, good sir!</font>

401
00:21:00,540 --> 00:21:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Of course, it will be problematic
if Granvelle raises a fuss at the capital.</font>

402
00:21:04,830 --> 00:21:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Have no fear!</font>

403
00:21:06,670 --> 00:21:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I made sure that he got a letter
warning against any funny business.</font>

404
00:21:11,580 --> 00:21:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And if he still refuses to sign the contract,</font>

405
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">then I'm certain that sending his precious
daughter's hand in the mail will convince him.</font>

406
00:21:19,710 --> 00:21:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Scumbags! They took Cecil hostage
to steal the mining rights?!</font>

407
00:21:24,130 --> 00:21:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's playing dirty!</font>

408
00:21:29,750 --> 00:21:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shit. She's awake.</font>

409
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We're almost to Carnel's territory.
Don't bother struggling.</font>

410
00:21:35,330 --> 00:21:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Might have to kick her
a few times before she gets it.</font>

411
00:21:38,420 --> 00:21:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I have to do something, fast.</font>

412
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've specced out my stats for PVP.</font>

413
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're going down this time!</font>

414
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Papillon! I choose you!</font>

415
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:51,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Put 'em to sleep!</font>

416
00:21:57,130 --> 00:21:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Nice, that's one down. We're off to a great start!</font>

417
00:22:02,210 --> 00:22:03,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It disappeared?</font>

418
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now for some payback!</font>

